From awareness to action — yoga continues to inspire a global shift towards healthier minds, stronger communities, and sustainable well-being. As the world embraces yoga beyond a practice and into a way of life, the journey now is about turning awareness into everyday action.

#AyushNews #InternationalDayOfYoga #YogaForHumanity #YogaMovement #MinistryOfAyush #WellnessForAll #YogaForLife #IDY2026 #GlobalWellness #YogaJourney

