Your body often gives subtle signs before asking for support. Weak core muscles, poor digestion, and frequent constipation can affect how you feel every day. Practicing Shalabhasana (Locust Pose) may help strengthen the lower abdomen, support digestion, and improve overall body strength.

#InternationalDayOfYoga #IDY2026 #YogaForHumanity #YogaForWellness #VoicesOfYoga

